<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>

<head>
    <title>Congratulations! Your Restaurant is Approved!</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: #333;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 20px;
            background-color: #f4f4f4;
        }

        .container {
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            background: #fff;
            padding: 30px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
            text-align: center;
        }

        .header {
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }

        .header h1 {
            color: #28a745;
            /* Green color for approval */
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }

        .verification-icon {
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }

        .verification-icon img {
            width: 80px;
            /* Adjust size as needed */
            height: 80px;
            /* Adjust size as needed */
        }

        .content {
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            text-align: left;
        }

        .content p {
            margin-bottom: 15px;
        }

        .restaurant-details {
            margin-top: 20px;
            padding: 15px;
            background-color: #e9ffe9;
            /* Light green background */
            border: 1px solid #28a745;
            border-radius: 4px;
            text-align: left;
        }

        .restaurant-details p {
            margin: 5px 0;
        }

        .footer {
            margin-top: 20px;
            font-size: 0.9em;
            color: #777;
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="header">
            <h1>Congratulations!</h1>
        </div>

        <div class="verification-icon">
            {{!-- Use a standard image format like PNG or JPG for wider email client support --}}
            <img src="{{verificationIconUrl}}" alt="Approved Icon">
        </div>

        <div class="content">
            <p>Dear Restaurant Team,</p>
            <p>We are thrilled to inform you that your restaurant, <strong>{{restaurantName}}</strong>, has been
                approved to join our food ordering platform!</p>
            <p>We are excited to partner with you and look forward to helping you reach new customers.</p>
            <p>Your restaurant is now live on our platform as of <strong>{{approvedDate}}</strong>.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="restaurant-details">
            <p><strong>Restaurant Details:</strong></p>
            <p><strong>Restaurant ID:</strong> {{restaurantId}}</p>
            <p><strong>Name:</strong> {{restaurantName}}</p>
            <p><strong>Address:</strong> {{restaurantAddress}}</p>
        </div>

        <div class="footer">
            <p>Welcome aboard!</p>
            <p>If you have any questions or need assistance, please do not hesitate to contact our support team.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>

</html>